<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">10. Birding</h3>



<p>More commonly known as birdwatching, birding is all about observing bird=
s in their natural habitats, often from afar with binoculars and equivalent=
 equipment. However, birdwatching is also not exactly the same as birding, =
as birding specifically means observing birds to identify species and other=
wise committing to some activities revolving around birds.</p>


