hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">15. Brewing Beer</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Over the past couple of years, brewing=
 beer at home has also become an increasingly popular hobby among beer love=
rs. And why not? It sounds super cool, it=E2=80=99ll probably save you a fa=
ir bit of money, you=E2=80=99ll learn so much about beer, and the next time=
 it=E2=80=99s someone=E2=80=99s birthday you have a pretty unique homemade =
gift to give.&nbsp;</span></p>



<p class=3D"has-global-color-7-background-color has-background">If you just=
