hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">22. Chess Playing</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Chess is a board game, but it deserves=
 its own spot on the hobbies list. It=E2=80=99s one of the world=E2=80=99s =
most popular games, and an incredibly old game, with even world championshi=
p competitions arranged. A game of chess can last for a short while or even=
 hours, depending on how the game strategies each player takes plays out.&n=
bsp;</span></p>



<p class=3D"has-global-color-7-background-color has-background">Chess board=
s come in hundreds of different types, like a <a href=3D"https://amzn.to/3f=
jUGFR" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow">gla=
ss chess set</a>, beautiful <a href=3D"https://amzn.to/39lGPLH" target=3D"_=
blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow">wooden chess and chec=
ker</a> combo sets or even <a href=3D"https://amzn.to/3u2KmGH" target=3D"_b=
lank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow">magnetic travel sized =
sets</a>.</p>



