hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">23. Collecting (Stamps, Rocks, etc.)</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Whether it=E2=80=99s stamps, coins, ma=
gazines or something else, collecting can turn out to be an interesting and=
 even a fruitful hobby. For example, the stamps you collect today, especial=
ly if you collect them from all over the world, can be worth a lot of money=
 in the future.&nbsp;</span></p>



<hr class=3D"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-accent-color has-alpha-c=
hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">24. Coloring</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Though it may sound like a child=E2=80=
=99s hobby at first, actually coloring is an excellent activity for adults =
as well, boosting your creativity while helping your body and soul relax. Y=
ou can draw the pictures yourself or buy a coloring book full of images to =
color. There=E2=80=99s countless great ones to choose from, or pick from <a=
 href=3D"https://amzn.to/3ffghiU" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noope=
ner sponsored nofollow">Amazon=E2=80=99s Top Sellers</a>.</span></p>



