<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">34. Flower Pressing</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Flower pressing also makes for some go=
rgeous d=C3=A9cor around the house or a gift to give a loved one. There are=
 a couple of methods you can use to press flowers, </span><a href=3D"https:=
//www.ftd.com/blog/create/how-to-press-flowers" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"no=
referrer noopener"><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">explained right here</=
span></a><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">, but the most important part is=
 choosing the right flowers to press.&nbsp;</span></p>



<hr class=3D"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-accent-color has-alpha-c=
hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">35. Gardening</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">A fun way to get closer with nature, y=
ou can find a lot of benefits coming from gardening. Although it=E2=80=99s =
plenty of physical work, which will keep you fit, it=E2=80=99ll also relax =
you. Not to mention, your yard will look so beautiful from your efforts and=
 you may even successfully grow your own vegetables and fruits to eat.&nbsp=
;</span></p>



<hr class=3D"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-accent-color has-alpha-c=
hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">36. Genealogy</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">In genealogy you study your family and=
 its history. In some ways it may be harder than many of the other hobbies =
on the list, at least once you get far back enough into your lineage. Howev=
er, it=E2=80=99s also incredibly interesting learning so much of where you =
came from and what=E2=80=99s in your genes=E2=80=94 not to mention some tra=
vel is likely to be included in your research!&nbsp;</span></p>



<p class=3D"has-global-color-7-background-color has-background">An easy pla=
ce to start is <a href=3D"https://fave.co/3ezVh2k" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D=
"noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow">Ancestry.com</a> where you can sea=
rch billions of records, plus they offer <a href=3D"https://fave.co/3db1KSD=
" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow">DNA test=
s</a> to delve deeper into your history.</p>



<hr class=3D"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-accent-color has-alpha-c=
hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">37. Glass Blowing</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">This is a technique for glass forming,=
 in which you first inflate a molten glass into a bubble of sorts by blowin=
g with a pipe, after which the bubble can be shaped. At first it may sound =
like a difficult hobby to have, but there are plenty of glass blowing class=
es available for those just starting out, where you can learn instructions =
and techniques, which you can then use to blow glass independently on your =
own free time.&nbsp;</span></p>



<hr class=3D"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-accent-color has-alpha-c=
hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">38. Go Kart Racing</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Did you know that many famous Formula =
One champions started out their careers with karting? Go-karting, it=E2=80=
=99s more recreational form, is a fun and adrenaline-pumping motorsport in =
which you drive around a track in a type of an open-wheel car that resemble=
s a formula car. You can go kart both indoors and outdoors, depending on wh=
atever type of tracks are offered where you=E2=80=99re at, with the suits a=
nd karts typically offered by the establishment.&nbsp;</span></p>



<hr class=3D"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-accent-color has-alpha-c=
hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">39. Golfing</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Golfing is one of the most popular hob=
bies out there, and for good reason. It=E2=80=99s a form of light physical =
exercise, takes you amongst beautiful nature and is easy to turn into time =
for socializing!&nbsp;</span></p>


