<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">40. Graffiti Art</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Though some may look down on graffiti,=
 even thinking it=E2=80=99s more criminal than it is a form of art, graffit=
i art is an amazing way to let your creativity </span><i><span style=3D"fon=
t-weight: 400;">and </span></i><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">your thoug=
hts flow in a way where it=E2=80=99s visible to the whole world around you.=
 Before you get started on making graffiti art your hobby, though, it=E2=80=
=99ll perhaps do you good to plunge into some research on </span><i><span s=
tyle=3D"font-weight: 400;">where </span></i><span style=3D"font-weight: 400=
;">it=E2=80=99s actually cool for you to go draw your graffiti art in.&nbsp=
;</span></p>



<hr class=3D"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-accent-color has-alpha-c=
hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">41. Hiking / Backpacking</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Hiking is a great way to maintain or i=
mprove your fitness while getting friendly with beautiful nature for hours =
at a time. Even if the sound of a physical activity after a grueling week a=
t work doesn=E2=80=99t sound appealing, hiking can be incredibly relaxing a=
nd refreshing. One of my favorites hikes was taking the <a href=3D"https://=
bucketlistjourney.net/insider-tips-to-conquering-perus-classic-inca-trail-t=
