<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">43. Horseback Riding</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Whether it be on a forested trail or a=
long the beach, horseback riding is another amazing way to enjoy time outdo=
ors and in nature. You can even take it a gallop further spending some time=
