hannel-opacity has-accent-background-color has-background">



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">44. Hula Hooping</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Not only is hula hooping something tha=
t was incredibly fun to try out as a child, but it=E2=80=99s a great form o=
f exercising for adults as well. By hula hooping, you can strengthen and to=
ne your body, especially around the core, but also hips and thighs, in addi=
tion to which it can also lead to improved flexibility. <em>As a fun tidbit=
:</em> hula hooping has actually existed as a form of exercise since the ti=
mes of ancient Greeks!&nbsp;</span></p>



<p class=3D"has-global-color-7-background-color has-background">You can buy=
 a traditional <a href=3D"https://amzn.to/2P37hTv" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D=
"noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow">exercise hula hoop</a> or go for s=
omething a little more snazzy like an <span id=3D"productTitle" class=3D"a-=
size-large product-title-word-break"><a href=3D"https://amzn.to/3w3LtYw" ta=
rget=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow">28 LED color=
 changing hula hoop</a>.</span></p>



