fully lost in trying to figure out how to put each piece together, challeng=
ing yourself and your brain as you do it. And once you=E2=80=99ve finished =
a puzzle, you=E2=80=99ll feel accomplished and satisfied, but also oddly bi=
ttersweet over the project ending. </span></p>



