<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">66. Painting</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Just like many other hobbies on the li=
st, painting is also a form of art that offers relaxation while allowing yo=
u to express yourself in a creative way. Only the sky is a limit to how and=
