<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">72. Rappelling (Abseiling)</h3>



<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">In some ways rappelling is the opposit=
e of climbing, as you will be going downwards instead of up. It can get qui=
te extreme depending on the surface you=E2=80=99re trying to rappel, but it=
 will also get in physical shape while exercising your mind.&nbsp;</span></=
p>



